7.4 Task Force on ClimateRelated Financial Disclosures (TCFD)

7.4

Task Force on ClimateRelated Financial Disclosure (TCFD)

The G20 Financial Stability Board’s Task Force on Climate- Related Financial Disclosure provides a uniform framework that companies can voluntarily use to report their climate- related risks and opportunities and disclose the correspond- ing information to investors, lenders, insurers, and other stakeholders. This Annex provides an overview of Siemens’ activities based on these recommendations and offers refer- ences to other sources of relevant information.